snippet.title: Venba - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Venba is coming to Nintendo Switch in spring 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/venba-switch/

Play as an Indian mother, Venba, who immigrates to Canada with her family in the 1980s. Players will cook various dishes and decipher long lost family recipes. Through branching conversations, explore a story about family, love, and loss.

#Venba #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
